metadata.name: WEBTREE PASS
metadata.description:
This pass grants access to holder special channels in WEBTREE discord.  
Some example channels:

- Alpha chat  
- Upcoming mints  
- Whale wallets  
- Icytools top mints  
- Genie sweeps  
- Premint links  
- Important tweets about NFTs and web3  
- Holder only giveaway (NFTs and ETH)

By holding this token, you will be the part of WEBTREE family and 40% of sales of this token will go to treasury wallet. And holders will decide how to invest this funds.
